20. the Municipal Budget Officer obligate the LDRRMF for expenditures which are related to disaster preparedness and management only;
21. the MDRRM Officer prepare a budget for administrative needs of his Office to be funded from the regular MOOE or Capital Outlay of the LGU;
22. the Municipal Mayor ensure the completion of a permanent and disaster-resilient evacuation centers where food packs can be stored under defined conditions with good storage practices;
23. the Municipal Mayor ensure the completion of facilities and storage areas for relief goods; and
24. the Municipal Mayor ensure procurement of supplies for food packs.
